  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial will include:

        -  Study period up to 7 months.

        -  Office visits monthly lasting approximately 1 hour.

        -  Blood Draws.

        -  Oral medication that is taken 2 times daily.

        -  Photographs and biopsies if agreed.
    </textblock>
